  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">At great risk of being left behind</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Since March, due to Covid, the needs of young people with special needs have been neglected by the Department of Education, as they are unable to study or receive therapies and services that are necessary to continue their education.  It is widely recognized that remote education is not adequate for this exceptional population. The project seeks to defend the rights of this under-served population by ensuring they receive some form of face-to-face education and other essential services.</narrative>
  </description>
